          <p class="text-lg">No kernel rebuilds, no application changes. Install, protected.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-lg mt-10">
        Powered by eBPF, Bomfather enforces zero-trust policies across cloud, data-centre, workstations, and drones alike.
      </p>
    </div>
